[quote]In 2001, audiences first met and fell in love with a twelve-year-old criminal mastermind named Artemis Fowl. Since then, the series has sold over seven million copies in the United States alone. Now, this phenomenally successful series is being translated into a graphic novel format.

For the first time, rabid fans will be able to see the underground fairy world, examine Foaly&#039;s incredible inventions, look inside Fowl Manor, and of course follow their favorite criminal mastermind as he plots and connives in glorious full-color panels that bristle with action.[/quote]
